ady doing something… anything… to be a part of the solution, then hopefully this can be your soundtrack. And if you’re not… then hopefully this can be your inspiration. Notable Lyrics Can’t you hear our children cryingWhy doesn’t it break your heartCan’t you see our people dyingWhen did this world get so dark?We’re not perfect but we’re tryingWe all need to play a part… Get familiar below, Listen, Enjoy and take some actions as you continue to lead your voice on #EndBadGovernance and A #NewNigeria… DOWNLOAD MP3 The post Banky W – “Talk And Do” ft. 2Baba, Timi Dakolo, Waje, Seun Kuti, Brookstone, LCGC appeared first on tooXclusive. Get all the Latest news, Breaking headlines,Sport, Education, Finance, Gists, Jobs, Music/Video, Technology and Top stories in real time in Nigeria and around the world. Banky W – “Talk And Do Lyrics” featuring 2Baba, Timi Dakolo, Waje, Seun Kuti, Brookstone, LCGC. STREAM/DOWNLOAD MP3 “Talk And Do Lyrics“ Intro Mastaa Banky W Can’t you hear our children crying? Why doesn’t it break your heart Can’t you see our people dying? When did this world get so… October 27, 2020 In "Entertainment" 2Baba andÂ Waje come with “Frenemies“. Music legend, Innocent Idibia is popularly known as 2Baba returns to the music scene with a new single titled “Frenemies”. The Hypertek boss teams up with female vocalist, Waje for this thoughtful song that talks a lot about betrayal. In these days of friend, the… June 20, 2019 In "Music/Video" Timi Dakolo is one of those names that has earned its place among the greats in the Nigerian music industry and here are 7 of his most essential songs. Timi Dakolo stands as one of those artistes who has carved his own proud niche and consistently makes refreshing music that… August 7, 2018 In "News"